            "chapterTitle": "Piety",
            "urn": 1600730,
            "body": "<p>Abu Umamah (May Allah be pleased with him) said: I heard Messenger of Allah (\ufdfa) during the sermon of the Farewell Pilgrimage saying, \"Be mindful of your duty to Allah; perform your five daily Salat, observe Saum during the month (of Ramadan) , pay the Zakat on your properties and obey your leaders; (if you do so) you will enter the Jannah of your Rubb\".<br/><br/><b>[At-Tirmidhi, who categorized it as Hadith Hasan Sahih]</b>.<br/><br/></p>",
